1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,090
Use these tools and think creatively.

2
00:00:03,201 --> 00:00:04,371
1.

3
00:00:04,560 --> 00:00:06,291
Believe it can be done.

4
00:00:06,560 --> 00:00:11,090
When you believe something can be done, your mind will find the ways to do it.

5
00:00:11,440 --> 00:00:14,931
Believing a solution paves the way to solution.

6
00:00:15,360 --> 00:00:23,171
Eliminate impossible, won't work, can't do, no use trying from your thinking and speaking vocabularies.

7
00:00:23,171 --> 00:00:24,451
2.

8
00:00:24,560 --> 00:00:27,331
Don't let tradition paralyze your mind.

9
00:00:27,440 --> 00:00:29,411
Be receptive to new ideas.

10
00:00:29,600 --> 00:00:30,931
Be experimental.

11
00:00:31,121 --> 00:00:32,610
Try new approaches.

12
00:00:32,880 --> 00:00:35,570
Be progressive in everything you do.

13
00:00:35,570 --> 00:00:37,570
3.

14
00:00:37,840 --> 00:00:41,010
Ask yourself daily, how can I do better?

15
00:00:41,360 --> 00:00:43,650
There is no limit to self-improvement.

16
00:00:43,760 --> 00:00:48,371
When you ask yourself, how can I do better, sound answers will appear.

17
00:00:48,641 --> 00:00:50,050
Try it and see.

18
00:00:50,560 --> 00:00:51,971
4.

19
00:00:52,240 --> 00:00:55,090
Ask yourself, how can I do more?

20
00:00:55,520 --> 00:00:57,891
Capacity is a state of mind.

21
00:00:58,161 --> 00:01:03,411
Asking yourself this question puts your mind to work to find intelligent shortcuts.

22
00:01:03,681 --> 00:01:10,691
The success combination in business is, do what you do better, improve the quality of your output,

23
00:01:10,800 --> 00:01:15,891
and do more of what you do, increase the quantity of your output.

24
00:01:15,891 --> 00:01:17,411
5.

25
00:01:17,600 --> 00:01:19,891
Practice asking and listening.

26
00:01:20,000 --> 00:01:24,931
Ask and listen, and you'll obtain raw material for reaching sound decisions.

27
00:01:25,040 --> 00:01:28,691
Remember, big people monopolize the listening.

28
00:01:28,880 --> 00:01:31,650
Small people monopolize the talking.

29
00:01:31,650 --> 00:01:32,931
6.

30
00:01:33,121 --> 00:01:34,451
Stretch your mind.

31
00:01:34,560 --> 00:01:35,891
Get stimulated.

32
00:01:36,080 --> 00:01:41,731
Associate with people who can help you think of new ideas, new ways of doing things.

33
00:01:42,161 --> 00:01:46,691
Mix with people of different occupational and social interests.

